sources.title: American Rap Stars - Full Movie
sources.description:
What was the state of hip-hop in the year 2002? Where was music headed and who were the artists making a difference? This documentary takes an in-depth look at the early-2000s hip hop scene, and features interviews and performances with some of the most important artists in the business, including Snoop Dogg, OutKast, Ludacris, Run-D.M.C., Jay-Z, Goodie Mob, The Roots, Russell Simmons and more.
